Class IndexProviderSubSolution

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.backend.IndexProviderSubSolution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexProviderElement

    public class IndexProviderSubSolution
extends java.lang.Object
implements IndexProviderElement
    This class represents a specific case of IndexProviderElement. It is used to represent a subsolution. An IndexProviderSubSolution assign for each solutions of a lower level, a List.
    Author:
    Cédric Andreolli, Chloé Boulanger, Olivier Cléro, Antoine Guellier, Sébastien Guilloux, Arthur Templé
